<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Refund Policy - Yourtickets</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="card shadow-sm p-5 border-0">
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-4">Refund and Cancellation Policy</h2>
            <hr>
            <div class="lh-lg">
                <p><b>1. Cancellation Timeline:</b> Agar aap yatra se 24 ghante pehle ticket cancel karte hain, toh aapko 90% refund milega.</p>
                <p><b>2. Last Minute:</b> 24 ghante ke andar cancellation par koi refund nahi diya jayega.</p>
                <p><b>3. Service Issue:</b> Agar bus hamari taraf se cancel hoti hai, toh aapko 100% refund milega.</p>
                <p><b>4. Processing:</b> Refund ki rashi aapke original payment method mein 5-7 working days ke andar bhej di jayegi.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Back to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
